{"tid":1211394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警犬向高等法院發射催淚彈","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:25:49.000Z","uid":127583,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3597caee4cd29f3a173a312923c913a6fc2c8e92","tid":1211394,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6點左右 班狗推到出力寶中心面向高等法院個陣<br />\n分別向太古廣場方向 中銀方向嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人群</span></span>發射催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n當時高等法院天橋同二樓平台亦有相當數量人群聚集 令人髮指嘅係 佢地漠視群眾安全 無視向法院射催淚彈背後代表住踐踏法治嘅意義 連續向二樓平台發射催淚彈<br />\n（留意返我張相完全係正面影 我隔離左右全部都係人）<br />\n一粒掠過左我頭頂喺人群身後面爆<br />\n一粒打高咗 可以好清楚聽到撞擊聲同見到火花 彈返落地面 但係絕對係同第一粒一樣瞄準二樓平台<br />\n好彩有一班手足即時用濕毛巾掩蓋住粒催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母香港警察 法院都夠膽射 仲好意思同我講法治 </span></span>"},{"pid":"b3bf3348df3e125a0a074d12908a014e4daac881","tid":1211394,"uid":6142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"從來都冇法治，只有人治"},{"pid":"119384c0f7aae9a28a7dde53c29d07862bde4556","tid":1211394,"uid":127583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b3bf3348df3e125a0a074d12908a014e4daac881","tid":1211394,"uid":6142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"從來都冇法治，只有人治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"好撚心痛 望住仲有咁多人未識死 識驚"},{"pid":"2a6cdebd444e4946fcb19ec8af21a114aa92618e","tid":1211394,"uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"347dba0138feea0572ae07bf7e882e2fadc88dff","tid":1211394,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"佢哋一定好憎法院啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd95fe885a516253bd0ffe28dff1a903cd334f62","tid":1211394,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,